edBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T02:08:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五毛狗出沒注意！9527~ #48157</span><br />\n五毛同雜種有親「習大大」+ 打殘體字</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/tg8us6vx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftg8us6vx&h=2fc572aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160423/845373/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20160423%2F845373%2F&d=t9lvrop9ljT%2F%2Fon6qZ%2B%2FxhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=e51841f0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160423/845373/</a><br />\n中共官媒過去為中國國家主席習近平打造親民形象工程，經常在報道或微博上稱呼他為「習大大」，其夫人彭麗媛則被稱為「彭麻麻」。<br />\n<ins><strong><em>大陸傳媒仲用「習大大」！</em></strong></ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://finance.sina.com.cn/stock/y/2017-04-26/doc-ifyetwsm0490871.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffinance.sina.com.cn%2Fstock%2Fy%2F2017-04-26%2Fdoc-ifyetwsm0490871.shtml&d=t9lvrop9ljT%2F%2Fon6qZ%2B%2FxhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=635f239e\" target=\"_blank\">http://finance.sina.com.cn/stock/y/2017-04-26/doc-ifyetwsm0490871.shtml</a><br />\n2017-04-26<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cppcc.china.com.cn/2017-04/12/content_40604898.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcppcc.china.com.cn%2F2017-04%2F12%2Fcontent_40604898.htm&d=t9lvrop9ljT%2F%2Fon6qZ%2B%2FxhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=5f5f5444\" target=\"_blank\">http://cppcc.china.com.cn/2017-04/12/content_40604898.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/bn8uelhs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fbn8uelhs&h=34597b6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2017-04-12"},{"pid":"2e3ef9d4ef6ec58ded4f9fe28b79a1137b56296e","tid":227163,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T